{"word":"πρόσφατος","slug":"πρόσφατος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πρόσφατος</b></el> <el>(πρός-φᾰτος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πέφαμαι</el>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> of *<a href='S:φένω†'><el>φένω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>lately slain, fresh-slain</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>generally, <i>fresh, recent</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><el>πρόσφατον</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> of Time, <i>recently, lately</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}